512,"uid":100131,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af23e52e5c4bfe3001284b125c555cf6fb157e82","tid":628512,"uid":134178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c2bf0f740d7b39118aeb1b371b8d34367ed34b6e","tid":628512,"uid":100131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T02:59:07.000Z","msg":"諗咩諗到抑鬱?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:03:54.000Z","msg":"睇我上一個post"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:23:46.000Z","msg":"this?<br />\n由細個已經開始有種被遺棄既感覺<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/621058/page/1?post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/621058/page/1?post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟手睇埋你另一個post<br />\n好想分手 但冇咁既勇氣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/618721/page/1?post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/618721/page/1?post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你同我以前細個一個鄰居似, 但又有分別, 佢老豆老粗, 夜晚全家等佢返黎食飯, 佢成日一見D餸唔啱食, 就反枱, D餸倒哂落地, 佢一條友出街食<br />\n<br />\n嗰時我細唔識野, 我地搬咗之後, 老母成日同我地講返.<br />\n<br />\n咁嗰家人有一個大女, 一個細仔, 聽講之後佢地離咗婚, 兩個都跟老母.<br />\n<br />\n個女廿中嘅時候搵咗三十中嘅老師結咗婚, 我老母話佢缺乏父愛, 搵個三十中嘅好正常, 咁先照顧到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41ef17e80bc1141eec3cb6cd3b083e35a325e881","tid":628512,"uid":115306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:30:13.000Z","msg":"自命抑鬱？<br />\n有冇諗過自殺"},{"pid":"e79e6743b17944cf39fe5dee312ae61f8c20d338","tid":628512,"uid":134178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41ef17e80bc1141eec3cb6cd3b083e35a325e881","tid":628512,"uid":115306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:30:13.000Z","msg":"自命抑鬱？<br />\n有冇諗過自殺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T04:36:35.000Z","msg":"睇醫生確診<br />\n有<br />\n初初個時好嚴重<br />\n日日都係到諗點死舒服<br />\n諗返個時世界彷彿係黑白色<br />\n個時真係覺得自己呼吸都浪費緊空氣<br />\n同埋我死左應該會普天同慶<br />\n但到最後企係露台都冇勇氣跳落去"},{"pid":"96710